{"parentUuid":"35a8afc6-a785-4e3f-82c4-586a4e2ef5a8","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01FRG3Th76tEXfwxhAmvnJ5c","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"In tmux, `Ctrl+K` from your terminal emulator won't clear the scrollback buffer. Here are the options:\n\n**Clear screen only (like `clear`):**\n```\nCtrl+L\n```\n\n**Clear screen + scrollback buffer:**\n```bash\nclear && tmux clear-history\n```\nOr bind it:\n```bash\n# In ~/.tmux.conf\nbind -n C-k send-keys \"clear && tmux clear-history\" Enter\n```\n\n**Just clear tmux scrollback (from command line):**\n```bash\ntmux clear-history\n```\n\n**From tmux command mode:**\n```\nPrefix + :  →  clear-history\n```\n\nThe key distinction: `Ctrl+L` only clears the visible screen. `tmux clear-history` wipes the scrollback buffer too."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2470,"cache_read_input_tokens":13947,"output_tokens":231,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2470,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZJGb2izdHuiokicuneSW","type":"assistant","uuid":"56498238-1b30-4582-884a-6171d9a8490e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:23:15.580Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"sdk-cli","cwd":"/Users/4thwithme","sessionId":"36eca803-ab8d-4795-a479-453ad72bab31","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
